Version:  1.0
Type:     pix/mwb


This package contains several icons and docks-anim for TimeConnect, all  in
the MWB style:


Short:    Phone Call coster/logger with MUI
Author:   jeffp@club-internet.fr (Jean-François PICK)
Version:  1.30
