@node MAGICAMINET.LHA "MAGICAMINET.LHA"

Short:    Sets of Icons for the CD-ROMs AMINET.
Uploader: egerard@club-internet.fr (Eric Gerard)
Author:   egerard@club-internet.fr (Eric Gerard)
Type:     pix/mwb


This package contains several icons for the CD-ROMs AMINET, all in the  MWB
style:

    - Individuals
        From Aminet 1 to 24

    - Aminet Sets :
        From 1 to 6.
             

This package is Email-Ware. If you like the icons and use  them  regularly,
you are obligated to send me E-mail (if you have E-mail access that is).

    E-mail: egerard@club-internet.fr


@{"Example" SYSTEM "SYS:Utilities/Multiview MagicAminet.IFF"}

@endnode

@node MAGICCOUNTRY.LHA "MAGICCOUNTRY.LHA"

Short:    Set of icons "localized" for developers
Author:   egerard@club-internet.fr (Eric Gerard)
Uploader: egerard@club-internet.fr (Eric Gerard)
Type:     pix/mwb


COPYRIGHT

This package is freeware. This means you can copy it freely as long as  you
don't  ask  any  money for it, except perhaps a nominal fee for copying. If
you like and use this package, please tell me!


CONTENTS

This archive contains many MagicWB-style icons :

    * AmigaGuide
    * Doc
    * Drawer
    * Install
    * Readme

Each icons have an flag representative of an country :

    * Dansk
    * Deutsh
    * English
    * Espańol
    * Français
    * Italiano
    * Nederlands
    * Norsk
    * Polski
    * Portuguęs
    * Swenska


@{"Example" SYSTEM "SYS:Utilities/Multiview MagicCountry.IFF"}

@endnode

